Task 6: avatars.js — Five Three.js Avatar Builders

SUMMARY:
Created js/avatars.js with all 5 Three.js WebGL avatar builders for the CyberSpark persona picker section. File is 494 lines.

IMPLEMENTATION:
Public API:
- initAvatars(): queries all .avatar-canvas[data-persona] elements, calls the matching builder, registers hover listeners, and uses IntersectionObserver to pause/resume rendering when the persona section scrolls off screen. Mobile guard: no-op if window.innerWidth < 640.
- disposeAvatars(): disconnects all IntersectionObservers, halts animation loops, and disposes all WebGLRenderers. Called before re-initialization on persona change.

Shared helper:
- _createBaseScene(canvas, accentHex): creates 160x160 WebGLRenderer (alpha, antialias), PerspectiveCamera, AmbientLight, DirectionalLight, and PointLight all keyed to persona accent color.

Five avatar builders (all use geometry primitives, no external textures):
1. buildExplorerAvatar — Astronaut: helmet (SphereGeometry), visor (CylinderGeometry), body, arms, 10 orbiting star particles. Accent: electric blue #3b82f6.
2. buildHackerAvatar — Cyber Skull Bot: box head, glowing sphere eyes with emissive pulse, jaw, antenna with glowing tip, 4 scanline planes with flicker animation. Accent: neon green #22c55e.
3. buildBuilderAvatar — Blocky Robot: box torso/head, rotating TorusGeometry gear on chest, box arms/legs, 6 sphere rivets, blinking head light. Accent: purple #a855f7.
4. buildDefenderAvatar — Armored Knight: CylinderGeometry armor body, sphere head, emissive visor, box shield with pulsing TorusGeometry glow ring. Accent: coral #f97316.
5. buildEntrepreneurAvatar — Rocket: ConeGeometry nose cone, CylinderGeometry body, 3 fins, flicker-animated flame cone, 2 orbiting gold torus rings. Accent: gold #eab308.

AVATAR_BUILDERS map keys: explorer, hacker, builder, defender, entrepreneur.

